""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
""
""Comments
""document-------->
""
""ctrl-c : comment a single line
""ctrl-x : un-comment a single line
""shift-v: select multiple lines, then ctrl-c to comment the selected multiple
""""line
""shift-v: select multiple lines, then ctrl-x to un-comment the selected
""""multiple line
""
""end----------->
"""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""

